{"tid":1517353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳港人仿效朱元璋把反共紙條藏在月餅 內地人來港購買可將港獨思想散佈全中國","createTime":"2019-08-30T02:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:02:18.000Z","uid":80630,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"915246a774f754d38f0bb0f838e11cfb57fd7c2e","tid":1517353,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"有傳香港各大餅家將反共紙條藏係月餅到，每年啲大陸人來香港買/買水貨代購<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>以月餅將港獨思想散佈全中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTmJr47QGjo8Bh8PkJmKEQQF4axdUsATtZN3asnO5oFxXG6KTyC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcTmJr47QGjo8Bh8PkJmKEQQF4axdUsATtZN3asnO5oFxXG6KTyC&h=e4dc646b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只是到了明代，中秋吃月餅才在民間逐漸流傳。據悉，吃月餅之所以在民間廣為流傳，還與明朝開國皇帝朱元璋有關。<br />\n<br />\n當時正值元朝末年，中原廣大人民不堪忍受元朝統治階級的殘酷統治，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">各類反抗活動紛紛湧現</span></span>。朱元璋藉此機會，便聯合各路反抗力量準備起義。但朝庭官兵搜查很嚴密，傳遞消息十分困難。軍師劉伯溫便想出一計策，到處散佈流言，說有冬瘟流行，除非家家戶戶都在中秋節買月餅來吃，才能避免。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">命令屬下把藏有「八月十五夜起義的紙條藏入餅子中，人們買了月餅回到家中，發覺裏面藏着紙條，上面寫着：「<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中秋夜，殺韃子，迎義軍</span>!</strong>」</span>，再派人分頭傳送到各地起義軍中，通知他們在八月十五日晚同時<strong>起義響應</strong>。到了起義的那天，各路義軍果然一齊響應，起義軍如星火燎原。很快，徐達就攻下元大都，起義大獲成功。明太祖朱元璋月餅起義就這麼流傳至今。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQTG1Zmi5qGgb5ONF6UOSfZwjZwJPRw6KFYQrCT6INdmmch1wrQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcQTG1Zmi5qGgb5ONF6UOSfZwjZwJPRw6KFYQrCT6INdmmch1wrQ&h=5d143275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>明太祖朱元璋月餅起義</strong><br />\n<br />\n消息傳來，朱元璋高興得連忙傳下口諭，在即將來臨的中秋節，將當年起兵時以秘密傳遞信息的「月餅」，作為節令糕點賞賜群臣。後來，朱元璋終於把元朝推翻，成為明朝的第一個皇帝，自然更加重視吃「月餅」的習俗，每到中秋佳節，必定分發月餅，讓全體將士與民同樂。此後，中秋節吃月餅的習俗便在民間流傳開來。"},{"pid":"58effe35ba88ae7c560567562659fe0e538f007a","tid":1517353,"uid":212246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:23:59.000Z","msg":"入面可以放QR code，提供返香港真實情況同埋debunk大陸假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd3fec2c80abe9480e727ac32ca3e0b27fc54ee","tid":1517353,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"美心月餅小左好多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二手券降哂價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355a61b2cad7a15369dd66822b3cabf9b15bd5bc","tid":1517353,"uid":148438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd3fec2c80abe9480e727ac32ca3e0b27fc54ee","tid":1517353,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"美心月餅小左好多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二手券降哂價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84715b7cc158cf2532cd45e054952d1418ca9d75","tid":1517353,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd3fec2c80abe9480e727ac32ca3e0b27fc54ee","tid":1517353,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"美心月餅小左好多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二手券降哂價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"反共搞到俾中國人抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b661ba3a575e8e6a606072ded9d630cb3a6fd50f","tid":1517353,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:02:18.000Z","msg":"買月餅=反中亂黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n把帽子扣上 整個中国<br />\n以後十四億人都唔敢食月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}